description:
Danny welcomes author, podcast host and Real Housewives fo Beverly Hills star Brandi Glanville to the show. They talk about some of her memorable moments on the past seasons, what's to come next season, helping launch Vanderpump Rules, Denise, Celebrity Big Brother, and LOTS more.
